is and what anything means.

01:25:26.040 --> 01:25:29.210
My name is Jonathan
Standing Bear.

01:25:29.210 --> 01:25:31.610
I feel the grief.

01:25:31.610 --> 01:25:34.970
I will not turn away
from this grief.

01:25:34.970 --> 01:25:39.440
I will welcome this grief.

01:25:39.440 --> 01:25:44.530
Tears will often flow, or
they will be there to flow.

01:25:44.530 --> 01:25:46.400
And rather than
allowing that happen,

01:25:46.400 --> 01:25:48.240
