01:25:53.200 --> 01:25:57.360
And it was a
terrifying experience.

01:25:57.360 --> 01:26:02.040
But so wonderful as a, kind
of, training of what it’s like

01:26:02.040 --> 01:26:06.770
to be in the unknown, which
is, of course, what life is.

