Earth are already here.

01:31:45.130 --> 01:31:47.740
All we have to do—well, who is this we?

01:31:47.740 --> 01:31:50.800
We need the perspectives
of different cultures

01:31:50.800 --> 01:31:54.460
in order to weave the story
for humanity of the future.

01:31:54.460 --> 01:31:58.020
We are oneness and yet we
speak different languages,

01:31:58.020 --> 01:32:00.530
we see different worlds.

01:32:00.530 --> 01:32:04.540
Our role then becomes
a role of service,

01:32:04.540 --> 01:32:07.220
serving that which
wants to happen,

01:32:07.220 --> 01:32:08.890
that which wants to be born.

01:32:09.250 --> 01:32:13.030
