01:32:27.250 --> 01:32:30.160
It wants to happen.

01:32:30.160 --> 01:32:33.570
And what I say to
the elders around them

01:32:33.570 --> 01:32:37.690
is I say, how can we ask
them to want their life when

01:32:37.690 --> 01:32:39.770
