01:32:46.360 --> 01:32:48.980
I said I don’t know
how to help people.

01:32:48.980 --> 01:32:52.200
Tell me how you want
to help yourselves.

01:32:52.620 --> 01:32:56.520
And your role is quite
like a baby being born.

01:32:56.520 --> 01:32:58.590
The mother does
most of the work.

01:32:58.590 --> 01:33:02.310
The baby does some through its
struggles, and moving around,

01:33:02.310 --> 01:33:04.340
but the mother does
most of the work.

01:33:04.340 --> 01:33:08.410
The situations that
we perceive as problems

01:33:08.410 --> 01:33:12.690
are actually an opportunity that
we have been given to remember.

01:33:13.890 --> 01:33:16.980
So to the elders in this room
today I want to say to you,

01:33:17.240 --> 01:33:20.580
I want you to want your life.

01:33:21.100 --> 01:33:22.780
You gotta want your life.

01:33:28.380 --> 01:33:31.580
